{
  "stem": "21349.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, you see, [CLEARS THROAT] I just went in-- it was actually not the Gestapo, the police department.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I reported to the police department, that was it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as time went on, in December, some people came back from the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they formed again a kind of congregation, and they organized themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I also helped organize themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They started again with the Jewish services and different things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I helped out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then about January, the Gestapo said that all the Jewish congregation have to send a representative, who has to come once a week or even more often, and to report to them about the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was appointed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't volunteer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Were you appointed by the Jewish community or the Gestapo?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, by the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to appoint someone to go to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But [CLEARS THROAT] before that, many things happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even in 1938-- I don't want to mix up the dates that much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yet when things got worse, especially after Czechoslovakia and Austria was invaded in 1938, [CLEARS THROAT] then the Jews from the smaller communities moved into the Bremen because they felt safer in a larger community.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no place for them to live.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So one family, whom I know very well-- members of this family are still alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They live in [INAUDIBLE] Brooklyn, and they live in [INAUDIBLE]-- [CLEARS THROAT] donated their house, which was a six story house, and many Jewish family moved in there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe 20 families moved in this home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it became the center of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It became the center for services and for immigration work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to tell them what they did.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
